verses.verse: <S%H8416>Praise<s%> <S%H1747>waits<s%> for <S%H430>you,<s%> God, in <S%H6726>Zion.<s%> To you shall <S%H5088>vows<s%> be <S%H7999>performed.<s%>
You who <S%H8085>hear<s%> <S%H8605>prayer,<s%> to you all <S%H1320>men<s%> will <S%H935>come.<s%>

<S%H835>Blessed<s%> is one whom you <S%H977>choose,<s%> and cause to come <S%H7126>near,<s%> that he may <S%H7931>live<s%> in your <S%H2691>courts.<s%> We will be <S%H7646>filled<s%> with the <S%H2898>goodness<s%> of your <S%H1004>house,<s%> your <S%H6918>holy<s%> <S%H1964>temple.<s%>

By awesome <S%H3372>deeds<s%> of <S%H6664>righteousness,<s%> you <S%H6030>answer<s%> <S%H430>us,<s%> God of our <S%H3468>salvation.<s%> You who are the <S%H4009>hope<s%> of all the <S%H7099>ends<s%> of the <S%H776>earth,<s%> of those who are far <S%H7350>away<s%> on the <S%H3220>sea;<s%>
Who by his <S%H3581>power<s%> <S%H3559>forms<s%> the <S%H2022>mountains,<s%> having <S%H247>armed<s%> yourself with <S%H1369>strength;<s%>
who <S%H7623>stills<s%> the <S%H7588>roaring<s%> of the <S%H3220>seas,<s%> the <S%H7588>roaring<s%> of their <S%H1530>waves,<s%> and the <S%H1995>turmoil<s%> of the <S%H3816>nations.<s%>

They also who <S%H3427>dwell<s%> in faraway <S%H7099>places<s%> are <S%H3372>afraid<s%> at your <S%H226>wonders.<s%> You call the <S%H1242>morning<s%>'s <S%H1242>dawn<s%> and the <S%H6153>evening<s%> with songs of <S%H7442>joy.<s%>

You <S%H6485>visit<s%> the <S%H776>earth,<s%> and <S%H7783>water<s%> <S%H7227>it.<s%> You greatly <S%H6238>enrich<s%> <S%H6388>it.<s%> The river of <S%H430>God<s%> is <S%H4390>full<s%> of <S%H4325>water.<s%> You <S%H3559>provide<s%> them <S%H1715>grain,<s%> for so you have ordained <S%H3559>it.<s%>

You <S%H7301>drench<s%> <S%H7301>its<s%> <S%H1417>furrows.<s%> You <S%H5181>level<s%> its <S%H8525>ridges.<s%> You <S%H4127>soften<s%> it with <S%H7241>showers.<s%> You <S%H1288>bless<s%> it with a <S%H6780>crop.<s%>
You <S%H5849>crown<s%> the <S%H8141>year<s%> with your <S%H2896>bounty.<s%> Your <S%H4570>carts<s%> <S%H7491>overflow<s%> with <S%H1880>abundance.<s%>

The <S%H3733>pastures<s%> are <S%H3847>covered<s%> with <S%H6629>flocks.<s%> The <S%H6010>valleys<s%> also are <S%H5848>clothed<s%> with <S%H1250>grain.<s%> They shout for <S%H7321>joy!<s%> They also <S%H7891>sing.<s%>
